(43, 7, 39, 23, 32, 15, 15, 'the Spirit, which they that believe on him should receive', 'Connection of the Spirit''s Outpouring', 'This connection highlights the theme of the Spirit being given to believers. Both passages emphasize the transformative power of the Spirit, with John referencing the Spirit to be received and Isaiah speaking of the Spirit being poured out.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
