(43, 7, 42, 40, 2, 5, 5, 'out of the town of Bethlehem', 'Connection of Bethlehem Prophecy', 'Both passages emphasize Bethlehem as the birthplace of Christ. John 7:42 references the scripture about the Messiah coming from Bethlehem, while Matthew 2:5 confirms this by stating it is written by the prophet.', 'prophecy', 0.398, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
