(43, 7, 42, 42, 2, 4, 4, 'the seed of David, and out of the town of Bethlehem', 'Connection of David and Bethlehem', 'Both passages emphasize the significance of Bethlehem as the birthplace of Christ, linking it to the prophecy regarding the seed of David. John 7:42 mentions that Christ comes from Bethlehem, while Luke 2:4 details Joseph''s journey to Bethlehem because of his lineage to David.', 'prophecy', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
